{"tid":975413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你冇錯 只係我戇鳩啫","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:27:47.000Z","uid":227029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"962f556a08973b91f2f792d841c296c07053f4c5","tid":975413,"uid":227029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"幾年前鍾意咗個女仔 一直都冇表白 &ldquo;佢一早就知道我鍾意佢&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n早幾個月前我終於開咗口 佢話比啲時間佢 之後佢一直對呢件事隻字不提 而我又好戇鳩咁等 而係呢段時間 佢依然繼續搵我 <br />\n<br />\n而我自己覺得 既然佢唔比個答案我 即係唔想同我一齊/唔想破壞呢段友誼 所以我都當冇講過 好似普通friend咁繼續傾計玩<br />\n<br />\n直至睇到另個friend post 同佢一齊去玩嘅相 睇到佢&ldquo;我本來鍾意個個&rdquo;同一個我唔識嘅男仔攬埋一齊 個一下我真係屌出聲呆撚哂<br />\n<br />\n我屌出聲 唔係因為佢同第個一齊 而係我點解當初會咁撚戇鳩鍾意咗一個咁嘅人 仲要鍾意咗咁耐&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你冇錯 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只係我戇鳩啫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝你呀 巴絲 入嚟睇哂我成篇鳩up&hellip;<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"dba7055e39d01234414eb1c717d97ae1544b45bb","tid":975413,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"女人唔比答案係幾仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吊住你先<br />\n但講真呢個年代男男女女唔咁樣做嘅可能先係少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13792f0aefc7bde89ced5ee99e23d88639ad1ab","tid":975413,"uid":89066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"深表同情<br />\n<br />\n我都有差唔多嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n及早逃4呀施主"},{"pid":"e2235c3c4a5dc656c54de92dd3bee9594a143c36","tid":975413,"uid":89066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b13792f0aefc7bde89ced5ee99e23d88639ad1ab","tid":975413,"uid":89066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"深表同情<br />\n<br />\n我都有差唔多嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n及早逃4呀施主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"逃離"},{"pid":"b43b253fddb0fec84039614c8d769e0262b67411","tid":975413,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}